WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.000
 Step by step EVA flower 

00:00:04.874 --> 00:00:08.800
 Template available in video description 

00:00:09.873 --> 00:00:10.873
 Cut the mold and draw on the EVA 

00:00:19.769 --> 00:00:23.700
 Cut the EVA 

00:00:31.354 --> 00:00:35.300
 Glue the flap according to the dashed line of the mold 

00:00:52.914 --> 00:01:00.900
 Warm petals with hair iron and wrap each petal with your fingers 

00:01:39.495 --> 00:01:45.400
 Wrap the entire EVA strip without glue 

00:01:57.113 --> 00:02:03.100
 Release the pressure of the curl of the flower, without releasing it completely, so that the petals are well distributed 

00:02:05.715 --> 00:02:11.700
 Pass the glue only at the end of the flower 

00:02:17.074 --> 00:02:22.000
 arrange the petals, and open the flower 

00:02:39.275 --> 00:02:44.200
 Pass glue under the flower to fix the petals in the tidy position 

00:02:56.000 --> 00:02:59.000
 Note: If you want a larger flower, increase the length of the mold 

